~9% more HP<br />
~10% more AC<br />
~3% more attack<br />
~1% more shielding<br />
<br />
Paladins get 1095mana, 30% healing focus, and 10% mana preservation.<br />
<br />
And this is CLASS SPECIFIC ARMOR.<<<br />
