But of course, that's balanced, right?</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>/sigh.. once again I made no claim that they are balanced completely. And your claim about getting manna and and focus effects is not comparing apples to apples. You cant compare that, warriors dont need it to function properly. Sure it gives some more utility, but at this point, heals are still the realm of the clerics, (duids too in some cases) and we are still bringing only utility to the table, not overwhelming power. You make a point that there really isnt much difference between the armor sets, but there IS a difference. I can agree that the warriors could use an upgrade, but then I also say that in the later post. <blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Thaak</b><br /><i>2) Any change to the current knight situation makes them undesireable. They have only JUST in POP come into their own become wanted and useful in groups. To reduce them in any way takes away exactly what groups want from them.<br />
