<br />
This game shouldn't be dumbed down to chimp level. Your exp penalty was removed LONG ago, which shows that your about as dumb as a brick. Your lower HP is easily made up by ONE stun or ONE heal or ONE lifetap. So please **** off.</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>Ok you got me on the exp penalty. I will be big enought to admit that. I started in 99' when there was one. /shrug I paid my dues. I think your lame attempt at a flame reveals your ability to think out complex issues. This last statement adds nothing to the conversation. Where I offered a possible solution, you attacked my idea without even an explanation as to how increasing the aggro generated by a war dumbs the game down. Sure, we can stun/lifetap to steal that aggro, my suggestion was that warriors should be able to do the same. I dont see the problem. <br />
