	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>khozik</b><br /><i>.. or I read this chart wrong..</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>- Warrior is using Vanazir, arguably one of the best weapons in the game. Monk is using some staff from a Plane of Fire mini. <---- Problem 1 with parse. You compare apples to oranges.<br />
