<br />
Now someone probably thought that if monk isn't tanking and neither is warrior, the monk will prolly do only a meager 10% more DPS with equivalent weapons and takeing out riposte AA and skill from the equation. This is quite true, warriors in my guild (similar amount of AA) with Blade of War do about same DPS as monks with the best weapons available pre time to them. <------ This is wrong, class balance issue.<br />
<br />
What this parse shows:<br />
- Warrior is a better tank than a monk. Duh!<br />
- Warrior is doing better DPS than a monk when both tank due in part to AA/abilities AND weaker weapon. Duh!</p>
	
	
	
